com.acs.audiojack

Class Track1Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acs.audiojack.Track1Data

  • public class Track1Data
extends java.lang.Object
    The Track1Data class is used to decode the track 1 data into fields specified by ISO/IEC 7813.
